channel.title: Go Baby Go Montana!
channel.description:
Hi Go Baby Go teams, families, friends, volunteers, therapists, and everyone in between! Just letting you all know that we have a new chapter in Montana! Please spread the word for anyone in need of a car. You can contact the chapter at gobabygo.mt@gmail.com. Thanks!!
-Bethany
